---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Studio" description="The Murmmers Press Studio: a private control panel, in development.">
  <section class="section">
    <div class="wrap prose">
      <p class="eyebrow">Private</p>
      <h1>The Studio</h1>
      <p>The Studio is the press’s private control panel: the production line rendered live from the pipeline, per-book screens, the author-intent writing surface, the gates queue, the daily digest, the calendar and the sales panels. It is in development and will sit behind access control.</p>
      <div class="studio-note">
        <p class="label">Reference</p>
        <p>The internal production-line map is the design reference. Its gates run G1 to G8, with lettered sub-gates at production.</p>
        <p><a href="/studio/production-line.html">Open the production-line preview</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
